            "compression": 0,
            "text": "<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"pt-br\">\r\n<head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\r\n    <title>Detalhes do Bug</title>\r\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/css/main.css\"/>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n\r\n<div><header id=\"site-header\">\r\n    <div class=\"header-left\"></div>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"header-center\">\r\n        <h1>☕ Spring Espresso Game Testing</h1>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"header-right\">\r\n        <form action=\"/logout\" method=\"post\" class=\"logout\">\r\n            <button type=\"submit\" class=\"button button-secondary\">Sair</button>\r\n        </form>\r\n    </div>\r\n</header></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wrapper\">\r\n    <h1>Detalhes do Bug #<span>14</span></h1>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"message-box success\">\r\n        <p>Bug marcado como resolvido!</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"card\" style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">\r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom: 15px;\">\r\n            <strong>Status:</strong>\r\n            <span class=\"status-badge\" \r\n                  style=\"background-color: #28a745; color: white; margin-left: 10px;\">Resolvido</span>\r\n            \r\n        </div>\r\n        \r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom: 15px;\">\r\n            <strong>Criticidade:</strong>\r\n            <span class=\"status-badge\" \r\n                  style=\"background-color: #f8e4a7ff; color: white; margin-left: 10px;\">Média</span>\r\n            \r\n        </div>\r\n        \r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom: 15px;\">\r\n            <strong>Sessão:</strong> \r\n            <a href=\"/sessoes/detalhes/125\">SessãoTesteBug3</a>\r\n        </div>\r\n        \r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom: 15px;\">\r\n            <strong>Data de Registro:</strong> \r\n            <span>09/06/2026 15:56:55</span>\r\n        </div>\r\n        \r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom: 15px;\">\r\n            <strong>Descrição:</strong>\r\n            <div style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; padding: 10px; background-color: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 4px; margin-top: 5px;\">BugBugTeste3</div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        \r\n        <div style=\"margin-bottom: 15px;\">\r\n            <strong>Anexo:</strong>\r\n            <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">\r\n                <!-- IMAGEM -->\r\n                <div>\r\n                    <img src=\"/uploads/bugs/Bug_14_S125.png\" \r\n                         alt=\"Screenshot do bug\" \r\n                         style=\"max-width: 100%; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 4px;\"/>\r\n                </div>\r\n                \r\n                <!-- VIDEO -->\r\n                \r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n                <!-- PODER RESOLVER ELE MESMO COM SESSÃO DE TESTES FINALIZADA -->\r\n        \r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <!-- AÇOES -->\r\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\">\r\n        <a href=\"/sessoes/detalhes/125\" \r\n           class=\"button button-secondary\">Voltar para Sessão</a>\r\n           \r\n\r\n        \r\n        <!-- REABRIR BUG -->\r\n        <form action=\"/bugs/reabrir\" \r\n              method=\"post\" \r\n              style=\"display: inline; margin-left: 10px;\">\r\n            <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"bugId\" value=\"14\"/>\r\n            <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"sessaoId\" value=\"125\"/>\r\n            <button type=\"submit\" class=\"button button-warning\" \r\n                    onclick=\"return confirm('Reabrir este bug?')\">\r\n                Reabrir Bug\r\n            </button>\r\n        </form>\r\n\r\n        \r\n        <a\r\n        href=\"/bugs/listar\"\r\n        class=\"button button-secondary\"\r\n        style=\"margin-left: 10px;\">\r\n            Voltar para Lista de Bugs\r\n        </a>\r\n\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<footer>\r\n    <p>Spring Espresso Game Testing. Um Software Open-source para a disciplina de Desenvolvimento Web.</p>\r\n    <p>Desenvolvido com café e paixão!</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</footer>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>"
          },
